- Use `@rendermode InteractiveServer` on every page
- Use `@attribute [Authorize]` (from Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization) on every page
- The _Imports.razor should already have the needed usings; if not, add them
- For real-time updates on the appointments page, use `StateHasChanged()` after DB operations
